tags.name: Chesil Beach
tags.note: Limited access May-Aug, for the benefit of breeding seabirds and shingle vegetation. In Sep-Apr it is permitted to use the seaward side of the beach but not the inner flank.

tags.name: East Beach
tags.note: Surface is sand nearest to the sea
